Hello everyone,

Greetings from I&AR Student Council!

If you are a designer looking around for an opportunity to create your next
masterpiece, here=E2=80=99s the good news as we are back with the annual *Y=
earbook
Cover Design Contest*.

The yearbook is an annual book designed by the I&AR team having the memoirs
of all the passing out students and the precious times they spent in the
institute. It is easily one of the most priced possession for any
graduating student and we present you a chance to be the cover page
designer for the same.
*Prizes worth Rs.2000* are up for grabs for the winner!

For any further queries, write to outreach@alumni.iitm.ac.in or contact
Dhruv Jain (7708045836)

*Deadline - 11.59 pm, 5th November, 2016*

Students from *any year* (and not just the final year) can participate in
this contest.

Design is a journey of discovery. Make the journey. Bring out the best.



